706
00:46:42,939 --> 00:46:43,803
Just a second.

707
00:46:43,906 --> 00:46:46,568
Wait... what's the big deal even
it's from Beijing?

708
00:46:46,672 --> 00:46:47,969
So arrogant.

709
00:46:58,206 --> 00:46:59,173
This is monkey...

