729
00:49:00,444 --> 00:49:01,877
Let's go, master.

730
00:49:04,944 --> 00:49:05,774
They...

731
00:49:07,445 --> 00:49:08,537
They're drunk.

732
00:49:08,644 --> 00:49:09,702
