739
00:49:30,578 --> 00:49:33,206
You should learn from them.

740
00:49:33,312 --> 00:49:37,146
Yes, I'll follow your orders, General.

741
00:49:37,246 --> 00:49:39,214
Are you confident?

742
00:49:39,646 --> 00:49:40,908
Absolutely.

743
