746
00:50:21,213 --> 00:50:24,410
How much longer?

747
00:50:26,513 --> 00:50:27,309
Do you know him?

748
00:50:28,014 --> 00:50:29,276
"To Master Wang"

749
00:50:29,780 --> 00:50:30,747
It's an invitation.

750
00:50:31,147 --> 00:50:32,205
Zhu Yifeng.

751
00:50:32,314 --> 00:50:34,282
